{"tid":2354082,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"跑馬地警署遭投擲汽油彈 涉案中年女子被控串謀妨礙司法公正 准保釋候訊","createTime":"2021-01-05T08:08:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T19:42:25.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fcb8ca73fc48c466f57e1fea5d2b9ba0e441a80e","tid":2354082,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:08:12.000Z","msg":"跑馬地警署去年3月遭人投擲汽油彈，警方經調查後，拘捕五名男子，控以縱火等罪。案中再有一名女子被控串謀妨礙司法公正罪，今日在東區裁判法院提堂。裁判官將案件一併押後至下月8日，以便控方準備將案件轉介區域法院。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官批准控方申請。被告獲准繼續保釋，但除了原本3,000元的擔保金外，另加不得離港、交出旅遊證件、在報稱地址居住，以及每周向警方報到等條件。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，警方在案中服裝店搜出涉案物品，並發現倪在洗手間內傾倒潤滑劑。他及後向警方稱，母親曾叫他「沖走啲嘢」。據資料顯示，警方上次並無將潤滑劑列作控方證物。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210105/WVGNBV4Z4BBFRECCEFJS7FW3RY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210105%2FWVGNBV4Z4BBFRECCEFJS7FW3RY%2F&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAG6%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=651b22c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210105%2FWVGNBV4Z4BBFRECCEFJS7FW3RY%2F&h=4b0c8c84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210105/WVGNBV4Z4BBFRECCEFJS7FW3RY/</a>"},{"pid":"142408b8318e7ad86571606ae555f7ac2e52f426","tid":2354082,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:12:01.000Z","msg":"<del></del>"},{"pid":"788ff0c24c934571e4b7dcd7ca60d2cd9832924e","tid":2354082,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:14:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d0751070009712de3674f081b4849cee7b028b","tid":2354082,"uid":19528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:16:14.000Z","msg":"告埋老妨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3202eb3bc4eda76